sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Utilisateur
    participant FE as Frontend Vue.js
    participant API as Backend Spring Boot
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant SEC as DGI SECeF

    U->>FE: Saisir facture
    FE->>API: POST /factures
    API->>DB: Verifications + calculs + numerotation
    API->>DB: Enregistrer facture + audit
    API->>SEC: Envoyer payload FEC
    SEC-->>API: ACK acceptee/rejetee
    API->>DB: MAJ statut transmission
    API-->>FE: Retour numero + statut
    FE-->>U: Affichage facture
